IT Network Officer IT and Telecom
SCHOOL ADMINISTRATION POST. SSAT (Middle East) is a well-respected Consultancy, working with a large educational foundation to open a new school in Mohammed Bin Zayed City, to start in September 2014. We are seeking staff members to start work with us from early May. Applicants should send their CV, a photograph, current salary, and the names and contact details of 2 referees to: hr2@ssat.me by Monday, 5th May. State the position you are applying for in the subject line of your email. Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted, and responses will be made as CVs are received. SSAT Website: www.ssat.me | The language used in the administration will be English.IT Network Officer - This senior position ensures the continuous operation of the ICT infrastructure and reports to the Business Manager. The Network Officer will have experience with Microsoft servers, management of a wireless network and other devices. A relevant ICT Degree from a recognized university and minimum 7 years of industry experience. Start June.Applicants should send their CV, a photograph, current salary, and the names and contact details of 2 referees to: hr2@ssat.me by Monday, 5th May. State the position you are applying for in the subject line of your email. Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted, and responses will be made as CVs are received. SSAT Website: www.ssat.me
